title: Can anyone tell me what this font is
content:
I have searched everywhere and cannot seem to find a match. Can anyone please let me know if you recognize it. Thanks

comments.content: Reminds me of [Stahls Tiffany](http://web.archive.org/web/20140830112723/http:/www.ffonts.net/Stahls-Tiffany-2000.font) but that's not it. There's also [Thunderbird Extra Condensed](http://web.archive.org/web/20140830112723/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/thunderbird).
